TI  - ACCLIMATION OF PHOTOSYNTHESIS IN RELATION TO RUBISCO AND NONSTRUCTURAL CARBOHYDRATE CONTENTS AND IN-SITU CARBOXYLASE ACTIVITY IN SCIRPUS-OLNEYI GROWN AT ELEVATED CO2 IN THE FIELD
